data.description: Energy efficient home with leased solar. Wood burning stove for those winter nights = low gas bill.  Swamp cooler, central air and heat. Pool.  Low maintenance front and back yard. Large RV parking. 12x12 enclosed horse stall with 24x48 turnout. Separate hay barn and tack room.  3 car garage, 1 converted into room with AC. 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths. Separate laundry room, large office.  Security system in place.
